OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) will no
OL,7,Flonger attend automatic alarms in most
OL,8,Fnon-residential buildings unless they
OL,9,Fare told a fire is definitely
OL,10,Fhappening.
OL,12,FThe organisation said the change will
OL,13,Faffect properties such as office
OL,14,Fblocks and industrial estates between
OL,15,F7am and 8.30pm - meaning the Brigade
OL,16,Fwill only attend the affected
OL,17,Fbuildings if a call is also received
OL,18,Ffrom a person reporting a fire.
OL,20,FOutside those hours, LFB will still
OL,21,Fattend all alarms in any building.
