OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,FThe new policy - which was originally
OL,7,Fannounced in May but has come into
OL,8,Faffect today - has been brought in to
OL,9,Fallow firefighters to spend more time
OL,10,Fand resources on other priorities,
OL,11,Fsuch as working on fire prevention
OL,12,Fwith local communities and increased
OL,13,Foperational training.
OL,15,FLFB says 99 per cent of automatic call-
OL,16,Fouts are false alarms - meaning less
OL,17,Fthan one per cent are genuine fires.
