OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,FAssistant Commissioner for Prevention
OL,7,Fand Protection, Craig Carter, said:
OL,8,F"Following a period of extensive
OL,9,Fengagement with our communities and
OL,10,Fstakeholders, we are now ready to roll
OL,11,Fout this new policy.
OL,13,F"We are here to keep London's
OL,14,Fcommunities safe, and we want to do
OL,15,Fthis as effectively as possible. We
OL,16,Fwill always attend an emergency and
OL,17,Fwill continue to attend an alarm at
OL,18,Fany premises where people sleep ` such
OL,19,Fas homes, hotels and prisons.
