OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,F"As outlined in our Community Risk
OL,7,FManagement Plan, reducing our
OL,8,Fattendance at false alarms will give
OL,9,Ffirefighters more time to focus on
OL,10,Fprotection and prevention activity,
OL,11,Fsuch as visiting our most vulnerable
OL,12,Fresidents and communities, fire safety
OL,13,Fchecks, as well as operational
OL,14,Ftraining."
OL,16,FThe Brigade said the change will bring
OL,17,Fthe LFB in line with almost every
OL,18,Fother UK fire service.
