OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,FBuildings exempt from the new policy
OL,7,Finclude hospitals, schools and listed
OL,8,Fheritage sites.
OL,10,FBetween April 2023 and March 2024, the
OL,11,FBrigade attended around 52,000 false
OL,12,Falarms generated by automatic fire
OL,13,Falarms.
OL,15,FFalse alarms are commonly caused
OL,16,Finclude poor alarm design or
OL,17,Fmaintenance, dust inside detectors, or
OL,18,Fsteam.
