OL,3,CFire Brigade to stop attending most
OL,4,Cautomatic alarm callouts
OL,6,FThe LFB is urging business to ensure
OL,7,Ftheir automatic alarm systems are
OL,8,Fcorrectly managed and maintained to
OL,9,Fminimise false alarms, as well as
OL,10,Fensuring that staff in businesses are
OL,11,Fsuitably trained to understand their
OL,12,Fresponsibilities under fire safety law.
